        public boolean shouldForceReturnIDLE()
        If the method returns false at the end of the IDLE animation the mob won't be forced to it's original position
        Returns:
        True if at the end of the IDLE animation the mob is forced back to it's original location. False if at the end of the IDLE animation the mob is not forced back to it's original location
